text: Silvia de Luna (born 10 October 1957) is a Guatemalan equestrian. She competed in the individual eventing at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Guatemalan female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Guatemala Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2007 Pan American Games Category:Competitors at the 1993 Central American and Caribbean Games Category:Competitors at the 2006 Central American and Caribbean Games Category:Competitors at the 2010 Central American and Caribbean Games Category:Competitors at the 2014 Central American and Caribbean Games Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
